item.title: CVE-2016-9091|2024-08-06T02:42:10.359Z -- symantec%20corporation -- blue%20coat%20asg
item.description: Blue Coat Advanced Secure Gateway (ASG) 6.6 before 6.6.5.4 and Content Analysis System (CAS) 1.3 before 1.3.7.4 are susceptible to an OS command injection vulnerability. An authenticated malicious administrator can execute arbitrary OS commands with elevated system privileges.
